segmentosSRT.text:
- Sit down!
- You planned all this, didn't you?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Anyway, your life's worth little now.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Me and my lover want more time
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: This case is in the way!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Whose is it? Get rid of it!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
Sir, it's mine.
I've got my things in it. Let me keep it.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Get it out of my sight then.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
It's just a bunch of puppets.
Get rid of them! This is war!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: They're not mine. It's how I make my living.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
- What are you doing?
- They're shooting!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: What did you think you were doing?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
Look at all the chili sauce.
Let me see your eyes.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
- Trying to kill him, or what?
- They're just kids.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Kids? Where did he learn that from?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: We don't know what's going on.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Do you expect me to believe that?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
It's sabotage.
Sabotage to the communal kitchen.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: And sabotage of the Great Leap Forward!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: That kid could not dream that up.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
- Are you going or not?
- No!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
- I'm telling you to go!
- No!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: How do you like my singing?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: She smashed the windows of the jeep.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: You can't keep them. Burn them!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Erxi is good with his hands.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: You've gone to so much trouble.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Dad! Mom! Has she given birth?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: But he was okay after the water.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: It was the water that did it.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13
